<span id="freeTextContainer3753192621278743823">This is the captivating story of the bubonic plague in a small English town in 1665. This is a part of history that should be told!! Written as a novel of historical fiction with a wonderful heroine.<br/><br/>I love this sad yet essentially uplifting story about a town that sacrifices itself by cutting off all travel and communication between their village and the other towns to contain the progression of the plaque. <br/><br/>It is based on true stories and superb writing -- told in the language of the times.<br/><br/><br/>***Al</span>
